description: Multi purpose Zing Drawstring Pouch features color-keyed stretch lycra top hem that allows the drawstring to slide smoothly and cinch tightly. Can be used in a bag for extra padding, worn on a belt through the reinforced web loop, or clipped to a bag, strap or belt using the sewn-on plastic snap hook. Hem colors allow color-coded organizing.
title: Zing 561-222 MPB1 Medium Pouch (Black/Blue)
